          <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab155\" href=\"/ir/private/\">個人投資家の皆さまへ</a></li>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab158\" href=\"/ir/management/\">経営方針・戦略</a></li>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab164\" href=\"/ir/calender/\">IRカレンダー</a></li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab165\" href=\"/ir/financial/\">業績・財務</a></li>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab171\" href=\"/ir/library/\">IR資料</a></li>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab176\" href=\"/ir/stock/\">株式情報</a></li>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab183\" href=\"/ir/publicnotice/\">電子公告</a></li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab184\" href=\"/ir/howto/\">IRサイトの使い方</a></li>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab185\" href=\"/ir/disclaimer/\">免責事項</a></li>\r\n            <li><a id=\"SEOMENUV2_Tab186\" href=\"/ir/ir_sitemap/\">IRサイトマップ</a></li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_796 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</div>\n  </header>\n  <main id=\"main\">\n    <div class=\"top_wrap\">\n      <div class=\"inner_wide\">\n        <div id=\"dnn_TopPane\" class=\"TopPane\">\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr782_ContentPane\"><!-- Start_Module_782 --><div id=\"dnn_ctr782_ModuleContent\">\r\n\t\r\n<div class=\"top_kv\">\r\n<div class=\"top_kv_slider edit_slick slick-slider\" id=\"slider\" slick-arrows=\"false\" slick-asnavfor=\"desc\" slick-autoplay=\"true\" slick-autoplayspeed=\"5000\" slick-fade=\"true\" slick-speed=\"1000\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"pc_area\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/kv_01_pc.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"sp_area\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/kv_01_sp.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"pc_area\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/kv_02_pc.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"sp_area\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/kv_02_sp.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"pc_area\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/kv_03_pc.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"sp_area\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/kv_03_sp.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"pc_area\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/kv_04_pc.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"sp_area\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/kv_04_sp.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"top_kv_cont\">\r\n<h1 class=\"top_kv_head\">Creating<br />\r\na Bright Future</h1>\r\n<div class=\"top_kv_lead\">抄紙プレスパートの<span class=\"sp_area\"></span>総合ソリューションカンパニーとして<br />\r\nサステナブルな明るい未来を創造</div>\r\n<div class=\"top_kv_desc edit_slick slick-slider\" id=\"desc\" slick-arrows=\"false\" slick-asnavfor=\"slider\" slick-autoplay=\"true\" slick-dots=\"false\" slick-fade=\"true\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"desc_main\">Technology &amp; Quality</div>\r\n<div class=\"desc_sub\">高度な技術力と品質</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"desc_main\">Contribution to Society</div>\r\n<div class=\"desc_sub\">抄紙要具事業を通しての社会貢献</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"desc_main\">Sustainability</div>\r\n<div class=\"desc_sub\">環境にやさしい紙作り</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"desc_main\">Global Strategy</div>\r\n<div class=\"desc_sub\">グローバル戦略</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_782 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</div>\n        <div id=\"dnn_ContentPane\" class=\"ContentPane\">\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr407_ContentPane\"><!-- Start_Module_407 --><div id=\"dnn_ctr407_ModuleContent\">\r\n\t\r\n<div class=\"top_philosophy\">\r\n<div class=\"left\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_philosophy.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"right\">\r\n<h2 class=\"top_heading sp_align_right\">Our Philosophy\r\n<div class=\"sub\">イチカワが目指すもの</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"sp_area sp_mt_md\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_philosophy.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"mb_0 sp_mt_md leading_loosest\">イチカワが目指すもの。それは「プレスパートの総合ソリューションカンパニー」として、最適な製品の組み合わせにより、お客様の抄紙機プレスパート能力を最大化し、その提供を通じて、「省エネルギー、環境にやさしい紙作り」に貢献することです。</p>\r\n<p class=\"mb_0 sp_mt_md\"><a class=\"link_btn bulge blue\" href=\"/corporate/topmessage/\">トップメッセージ</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_407 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr852_ContentPane\"><!-- Start_Module_852 --><div id=\"dnn_ctr852_ModuleContent\">\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_852 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"inner_wide\">\n      <div id=\"dnn_Content01Pane\" class=\"Content01Pane\">\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr783_ContentPane\"><!-- Start_Module_783 --><div id=\"dnn_ctr783_ModuleContent\">\r\n\t\r\n<div class=\"top_pickup\">\r\n<div class=\"left\">\r\n<div class=\"top_heading\">Pick Up\r\n<div class=\"sub\">ピックアップ</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"right\">\r\n<div class=\"top_pickup_slider edit_slick slick-slider\" slick-infinite=\"false\" slick-variablewidth=\"true\" slick-dots=\"true\"><a class=\"link\" href=\"/ir/management/vision/\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_pickup_01.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Long-term Vision</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">長期ビジョン</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a><a class=\"link\" href=\"/ir/management/plan/\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_pickup_02.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Mid-term<br />\r\nManagement Plan</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">中期経営計画</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a><a class=\"link\" href=\"/sustainability/environment/policy/\">\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_pickup_03.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Environmental Management Systems</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">環境マネジメント</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_783 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</div>\n      <div id=\"dnn_Content02Pane\" class=\"Content02Pane\">\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr784_ContentPane\"><!-- Start_Module_784 --><div id=\"dnn_ctr784_ModuleContent\">\r\n\t\r\n<div class=\"top_news\">\r\n<h2 class=\"top_heading align_right\">News Release\r\n<div class=\"sub\">ニュースリリース</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<a class=\"top_news_notice\" href=\"#.pdf\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n<div class=\"label\">重要なお知らせ</div>\r\n<div class=\"date\">2024年00月00日</div>\r\nこの文章はダミーです。文字の大きさ、量、字間、行間等を確認するために入れています。</a>\r\n<!-- NewsStart -->\r\n<div id=\"dnn_ctr544_ModuleContent\">\r\n<div class=\"ViewAnnouncements\" id=\"dnn_ctr544_ViewAnnouncements_pnlAllArea\">\r\n<div class=\"icmdtp-newsItem\">\r\n<!-- xj-contents // -->\r\n<ul class=\"news_list mt_md\" id=\"xj-mainlist\"></ul>\r\n<!-- // xj-contents -->\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- NewsEnd -->\r\n<ul class=\"top_news_link\">\r\n    <li><a class=\"link_btn bulge\" href=\"/release/\">ニュースリリース一覧</a></li>\r\n    <li><a class=\"link_btn bulge\" href=\"/products/event/\">イベント・展示会</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_784 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"top_wrap middle\">\n      <div class=\"inner_wide\">\n        <div id=\"dnn_Content03Pane\" class=\"Content03Pane\">\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr785_ContentPane\"><!-- Start_Module_785 --><div id=\"dnn_ctr785_ModuleContent\">\r\n\t\r\n<div class=\"top_focus\">\r\n<h2 class=\"top_heading align_center\">Focus on IK\r\n<div class=\"sub\">イチカワについて</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"mt_md align_center leading_loosest\">皆さまに当社への理解をより深めていただけるように、<span class=\"pc_area\"></span>当社の強みや目指す姿、販売体制等をわかりやすくご説明いたします。</p>\r\n<div class=\"top_focus_link\"><a class=\"link\" href=\"/focus_on/press_part/#head_press\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_focus_01.jpg\" />\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Paper Making Process &amp;<br />\r\nPress Part</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">抄紙工程とプレスパート</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a><a class=\"link\" href=\"/focus_on/market/#head_market\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_focus_02.jpg\" />\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Markets &amp;<br />\r\nStrengths</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">マーケットと強み</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a><a class=\"link\" href=\"/focus_on/sales_system/#head_sales\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_focus_03.jpg\" />\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Sales Structure &amp;<br />\r\nMajor Customers</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">販売体制と主要取引先</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a></div>\r\n<p class=\"mt_md align_center\"><a class=\"link_btn bulge blue\" href=\"/focus_on/press_part/\">Focus on IK</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_785 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</div>\n        <div id=\"dnn_Content04Pane\" class=\"Content04Pane\">\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr786_ContentPane\"><!-- Start_Module_786 --><div id=\"dnn_ctr786_ModuleContent\">\r\n\t\r\n<div class=\"top_products\">\r\n<h2 class=\"top_heading align_center\">Products\r\n<div class=\"sub\">製品情報</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"mt_md align_center leading_loosest\">イチカワは、プレスパートの総合ソリューションカンパニーとして、高機能製品を提供し続け、<span class=\"pc_area\"></span>国内はもとより、海外からも高い評価を受けております。</p>\r\n<div class=\"top_products_link\"><a class=\"link\" href=\"/products/felt/\" data-bg=\"1\">\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Felt for<br />\r\nPaper Making</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">抄紙用フエルト</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a><a class=\"link\" href=\"/products/belt/shoepressbelt/\" data-bg=\"2\">\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Belt for<br />\r\nPaper Making</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">抄紙用ベルト</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a><a class=\"link\" href=\"/products/industry/\" data-bg=\"3\">\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<div class=\"main\">Industrial<br />\r\nProducts</div>\r\n<div class=\"sub\">工業用製品</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</a></div>\r\n<p class=\"mt_md align_center\"><a class=\"link_btn bulge blue\" href=\"/products/\">製品情報</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_786 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</div>\n        <div id=\"dnn_Content05Pane\" class=\"Content05Pane\">\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr787_ContentPane\"><!-- Start_Module_787 --><div id=\"dnn_ctr787_ModuleContent\">\r\n\t\r\n<div class=\"top_development\">\r\n  <div class=\"top_development_heading\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"top_heading\">Engineering &amp;<br />\r\n      Manufacturing\r\n      <div class=\"sub\">技術・製造</div>\r\n    </h2>\r\n    <p class=\"mb_0 txt_md leading_loosest\">新素材をはじめ、最新鋭の分析機器、製造機器に至る幅広い分野の技術情報を基に将来の実用化を見据えた開発試作、データ蓄積を行っています。</p>\r\n    <a class=\"link_btn bulge blue\" href=\"/development/\">技術・製造</a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"top_development_item\">\r\n    <div class=\"top_development_link\">\r\n      <a class=\"link\" href=\"/development/research_institute/\" data-bg=\"1\">\r\n        <div class=\"img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Portals/0/images/index/img_development_01.jpg\" /></div>